<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">

  <!-- Heading -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 max-w-3xl">
      Here you’ll find answers to common questions about using our platform.
      If you’re new, this section will help you understand how everything works.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">

    <!-- FAQ 1 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        What is this platform and how does it work?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        This is a multi-vendor blogging platform where users can create accounts,
        write blog posts, and earn based on how their content performs.
        You publish articles, readers interact with them, and your activity is tracked
        through your dashboard.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 2 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        Do I need an account to read or publish blogs?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        You can read public blogs without an account.
        However, to write, publish, like, or earn from blogs,
        you must create an account and log in.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 3 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        How do I publish my first blog?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        After logging in, go to your dashboard and click on
        <strong>Create Blog</strong> or <strong>New Article</strong>.
        Write your content, add images if needed, select a category,
        and publish when you’re ready.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 4 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        What kind of content is allowed on this platform?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        All content must be original, respectful, and legal.
        We do not allow copied content, hate speech, harmful material,
        or misleading information.
        Posts that violate guidelines may be removed.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 5 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        How are views, likes, and engagement counted?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        Views are counted when readers open your article.
        Likes and other interactions are recorded in real time.
        All statistics are shown in your dashboard so you can track performance easily.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 6 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        How do earnings work on this platform?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        Earnings are calculated based on article performance,
        such as views and engagement.
        Your total earnings and daily stats are visible in your dashboard.
        The better your content performs, the more you can earn.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 7 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        When and how can I withdraw my earnings?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        Once you reach the minimum withdrawal amount,
        you can request a withdrawal from your account settings.
        Withdrawals are reviewed and processed securely.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 8 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        Can my blog or account be removed?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        Yes. Accounts or blogs that repeatedly violate platform rules
        may be restricted or removed.
        We recommend following content guidelines to avoid any issues.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 9 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        How do I update my profile information?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        Go to your dashboard and open the profile or settings section.
        From there, you can update your name, profile image,
        bio, password, and other account details.
      </p>
    </details>

    <!-- FAQ 10 -->
    <details class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-5">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-gray-900">
        What should I do if I face an issue or need help?
      </summary>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
        If you face any issues, visit the Help or Support section.
        You can also contact our support team for assistance.
        We’re here to help you grow and succeed on the platform.
      </p>
    </details>

  </div>

</section>
